    "body": "We can't really enable ATS right now because we have a DApp browser built-in which allows any URL.\r\nEven though it makes sense to disallow plain-http connections for normal users, DApp developers might want to use it and I think it should exist as an option.\r\n\r\nSo, I would close this one as a choice we make \"by design\".",
